<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.11">
<l>aṅṅaṉam tīmaikaḷ ceyvarka ḷōnampī yāyar maṭamak kaḷaip</l>
<l>paṅkaya nīrkuṭain tāṭukiṉ ṟārkaḷpiṉ ṉēceṉ ṟoḷitti runtu</l>
<l>vaṅkavar pūntukil vārikkoṇ ṭiṭṭara vēriṭai yāri rappa</l>
<l>maṅkainal līrvan tukoṇmi ṉeṉṟumara mēṟi yiruntāy pōlum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Young man, do [others] do such mischief to simple herder girls?</l>
<l>Being hidden, following after those who were bathing</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] diving into the water with lotuses,</l>
<l>Having grabbed and taken away their flowery saris,</l>
<l rend="indent">as those with cobra-like mounds of Venus begged,</l>
<l>It seems you were up in a tree, saying, “Fine ladies,</l>
<l rend="indent">come [up] and get [them]!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
